2019-12-17 17:47:26	--	- SINISALO, (ANNA) JOHANNA (1958-), a Finnish science fiction
2019-12-17 17:47:26	--	- and fantasy novelist and a script writer. Her novel 'Not
2019-12-17 17:47:26	--	- Before Sundown' (orig. 'Ennen päivänlaskua ei voi'
2019-12-17 17:47:26	--	- published in Finnish in 2000, when it also won the biggest
2019-12-17 17:47:26	--	- literature award of Finland) was awarded The James Tiptree
2019-12-17 17:47:26	--	- Jr. award in 2004.  She was nominated for a Nebula award in
2019-12-17 17:47:26	--	- 2009 for her short story Baby Doll.  Their most recent work
2019-12-17 17:47:26	--	- includes screenwriting for the film 'Iron Sky'.
